        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Zend_Rest_Route maps REST actions to request, bases on \"_server\" hidden field\/X-HTTP-Method-Override, but not request methods.\nIn that case, Zend_Controller_Request_Http::isPut() and Zend_Controller_Request_Http::isDelete() methods will return false.\n\nAlso, Zend_Rest_Route doesn't map a DELETE request method, so deleteAction() will never be invoked."
        },
